<header>
  <div class="header-title">
    <h6>
      Stations Dashboard
  </div>
</header>
<p>There are <%= @stations.total_stations %> bike share stations</p>
<p>Average bikes per station: <%= @stations.average_bikes%></p>
<p>The most bikes available at any station: <%= @stations.most_bikes %></p>
<p>The station(s) with the most bikes available:
  <ul>
    <% @stations.most_station.each do |s| %>
      <li><%= s.name %> (<%= s.dock_count %>)</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
</p>
<p>The fewest bikes available at any station: <%= @stations.fewest_bikes %></p>

<p>The station(s) with the fewest bikes available:
  <ul>
    <% @stations.fewest_station.each do |s| %>
      <li><%= s.name %> (<%= s.dock_count %>)</li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
</p>
<p>The newest staton is <%= @stations.newest_station.name %> - Installed: <%= format_date(@stations.newest_station.installation_date) %></p>
<p>The oldest staton is <%= @stations.oldest_station.name %> - Installed: <%= format_date(@stations.oldest_station.installation_date) %></p>
